    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pixeria's waffle supply has been stolen!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Super Pixeria is a 2D collectathon platformer with 100 waffles to collect across 10+ worlds! There are a variety of different locations and challenges, ranging from relaxing, simple objectives to challenging platforming gauntlets requiring determination to pass! Leap over spikes, dash across large gaps, and stomp on slimes as you follow the path to defeat the EVIL Mr. Pix! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This labor of love from the sole developer of Gruntioli Studios has waited years to be played and enjoyed. Made with both speedrunners and casual players in mind, there is something for everyone to enjoy in the world of Pixeria. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 100 Collectable Waffles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Unique Worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 Distinct Costumes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An Original Soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171080/extras/79399bde7ca8e7c880f452e8fc833fc1.avif?t=1749617725\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171080/extras_big/79399bde7ca8e7c880f452e8fc833fc1.avif?t=1749617725 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p></li></ul>",
